    "summary": "EXPERIENCE, AMBITION AND DRIVE:\nExtended (inter)national business &amp; teaching experiences make me suitable for a range of challenging freelance assignments. \nSince 2003 I work in the Benelux as professional Freelancer holding a Master of Science (Ir.) degree in Mechatronics and Bachelor of Science (Ing.) in Electro-mechanics. I gained a lot of experience as entrepreneur, (Design for) Lean Six Sigma Black Belt (DfLSS), Interim change manager, Business process improver, program/project manager, business consultant, Master and Bachelor lecturer and Trainer/coach.\nBefore my Entrepreneurship I engaged with several (inter)national top management positions with multinationals located in America, Europe and South East Asia. My key business assignments included functions as Plant Manager, Director Operations, Business Unit Manager, Factory Manager and Production Manager. \nAs DfLSS black belt, I am interested in adding significant value to cost saving projects applying the robust and well-known DfLSS methodology.\nAssignments associated with the continuous development of sustainable energy or the creation of a \u2018Greener\u2019 environment always get my special attention and preference.\nPeople &amp; leadership skills keeping the right balance between human &amp; task relationships. Team player able to adapt in various cultural business environments from SME to multinationals. \nResult oriented process approach based on data collection and analysis, combined with excellent communication skills, flexibility, drive and a high level of interpersonal and group commitment.\nLinguistic mastering Dutch (Native), English, French, German, Spanish, Portuguese and Polish.\nBenelux Entrepreneur since 2003 owning two companies: Best Facility Management BVBA in Belgium and Best Facility Management in The Netherlands.\nContact me if you want quality services and support, leading to enhanced, measurable and sustainable results.\n\nSpecialties: Interim change manager, (Design for) Six Sigma black belt, Program manager, Business consultant, Business process improver, Master & Bachelor lecturer, Trainer/coach, Master and Bachelor of Science engineer, Manufacturing Excellence, Prince2, European Business Excellence Model, INK-Business Model, Total Quality Management, Statistical Process Control, ISO 9000&14000, Minitab, MindManager",
